{{Top|leg}}
The '''Five Families of [[Cestus Cybernetics]]''' consisted of five politically powerful families on the planet [[Ord Cestus/Legends|Ord Cestus]]. They ruled the planet following the decline of the [[X'Ting]] population, and any one member could veto any business proposition on the planet.

They were killed when the [[Advanced Recon Commando/Legends|ARC Trooper]] [[Jangotat|A-98]] sacrificed himself by transmitting his beacon location from within their private bunker to [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Republic]] vessels in orbit, who proceeded to fire on and destroy the bunker. Afterwards, a planetary [[Regent/Legends|regent]] took their place.

